  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game time: <strong>1 hour + secret content</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short but intense story about a terrible incident in an abandoned house.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the guard woke up, he realized he was not alone in the house. But it was already too late...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668540/extras/c10bd4789c10eb536151e23376270504.poster.avif?t=1733664076\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668540/extras/c10bd4789c10eb536151e23376270504.webm?t=1733664076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668540/extras/c10bd4789c10eb536151e23376270504.mp4?t=1733664076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story also touches upon another character who was just walking on the outskirts of the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He heard some sound and came closer to the house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But when he found himself inside, it became clear that it was a trap and there was no way to get out...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668540/extras/c8048438f850ccddc30e8a31916ca83d.poster.avif?t=1733664076\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668540/extras/c8048438f850ccddc30e8a31916ca83d.webm?t=1733664076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668540/extras/c8048438f850ccddc30e8a31916ca83d.mp4?t=1733664076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>SECRET CONTENT</i></strong>: to get instructions and open all secrets - <u>you need to complete the game once or twice</u>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Told about two different characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nice graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easter eggs on popular games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel mini-games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmosphere of the 80s</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Moral story</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game time: <strong>1 hour + secret content</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short but intense story about a terrible incident in an abandoned house.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the guard woke up, he realized he was not alone in the house. But it was already too late...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668540/extras/c10bd4789c10eb536151e23376270504.poster.avif?t=1733664076\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668540/extras/c10bd4789c10eb536151e23376270504.webm?t=1733664076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668540/extras/c10bd4789c10eb536151e23376270504.mp4?t=1733664076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story also touches upon another character who was just walking on the outskirts of the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He heard some sound and came closer to the house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But when he found himself inside, it became clear that it was a trap and there was no way to get out...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668540/extras/c8048438f850ccddc30e8a31916ca83d.poster.avif?t=1733664076\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668540/extras/c8048438f850ccddc30e8a31916ca83d.webm?t=1733664076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2668540/extras/c8048438f850ccddc30e8a31916ca83d.mp4?t=1733664076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>SECRET CONTENT</i></strong>: to get instructions and open all secrets - <u>you need to complete the game once or twice</u>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Told about two different characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nice graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easter eggs on popular games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel mini-games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmosphere of the 80s</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Moral story</p></li></ul>",
